data.description: SELLER OFFERING $5,000 CREDIT AT CLOSING!! This immaculate turn-key townhouse located in Trilogy of Sunstone offers the ultimate in relaxed, yet luxurious living with its 2 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a generous 1,682 square feet of open living space. The gourmet kitchen is a standout feature, featuring stunning granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and tons of storage within beautiful shaker cabinets. Water softener, RO system, and $75K in upgrades throughout! Beyond the walls of this elegant home, you'll find an exceptional lifestyle awaiting you. Trilogy of Sunstone community is a 55+ community thats bursting with opportunity ands leisure. Here, you'll discover a world of unparalleled amenities, including a stunning pool, rejuvenating spa, inviting community center, state-of-the-art fitness facility, versatile sport courts, and endless miles of scenic walking trails. There's never a dull moment in this thriving oasis of leisure and recreation.
